headline: AES Rides on Renewable Expansion, Declining Wholesale Prices Ail
summary: AES is projected to gain from expanding renewable generation and decreasing carbon emissions from its portfolio amid the impacts of declining wholesale prices.

headline: CDT Insider Sentiment November 2024: Free To Move About The Cabin
summary: Since Trump became President-elect, the market is up +4.5% and the breadth of the market rally has been impressive. Insiders have endorsed the post-election rally with sentiment above normal
